text.tspan: It's a pumpkin, but it tastes like apple and bit of pumpkin.
Has a similar gut of apple as well.
Tastes sweeter than Earth's apple, has citric sourness
and little bit of GURIH (umami) in it.
From / Dari: Botanic Divisionate, Govt. of Dasandim, Dasandim
For / Untuk: Emprs. Fibell Luxbell, Snoworld
